## Threshold status legend
- `BELOW`: pending_count < `learn_threshold`. Improvements accumulate; no action.
- `AT_THRESHOLD`: pending_count = `learn_threshold`. Next correction (or explicit `TRIGGER`) will fire `improvement_proposal.md` and signal phase 13.7.
- `ABOVE`: pending_count > `learn_threshold`. Proposal already pending; phase 13.7 should run.
